							Medium
						</a>
						<a href="/blog" class="hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors font-bold">Blog</a>
						<a href="/shop" class="hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors font-bold text-accent-purple">Shop</a>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 border-l border-white/10 pl-6">
